{title: 貴きみかみよ}
{subtitle: Aus tiefer Not (Luther, 1523) — Japanese, 讃美歌 (1931) no. 250, tr. 中山昌樹}
{key: Am}
{time: 4/4}
{tempo: 64}
{comment: Luther's penitential psalm hymn (Psalm 130), "Out of the depths I cry to you"}

{start_of_verse: 1}
[Am]たふとき[Dm]みかみよ [G]なやみの[C]ふちより
tautoki mikami yo, nayami no fuchi yori
[Am]よばはる[Dm]わが身を [E]かへりみた[Am]まへや
